// Lucide / Feather style paths (mostly fill="none" stroke="currentColor")
---

<svg
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width={size}
    height={size}
    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    fill="none"
    stroke="currentColor"
    stroke-width="2"
    stroke-linecap="round"
